## TTS ‚Äî oc-speak.sh (server-based)

Wrapper: `scripts/oc-speak.sh` ‚Äî POSTs to pc-agent `/voice/speak-async` (runs `friday-speak.py` on the machine hosting the agent).

**ALWAYS async / fire-and-forget. Never block.**

```bash
$OPENCLAW_HOME/scripts/oc-speak.sh "text to speak"
$OPENCLAW_HOME/scripts/oc-speak.sh "text to speak" 1
$OPENCLAW_HOME/scripts/oc-speak.sh "text to speak" 1 subagent
$OPENCLAW_HOME/scripts/oc-speak.sh "text to speak" 1 "" thinking
```

### Session voice check

```bash
python3 skill-gateway/scripts/pick-session-voice.py --check
```

