## WhatsApp (Evolution API)

```bash
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8181/message/sendText/openclaw \
  -H "apikey: $EVOLUTION_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"number": "917870455443", "text": "Hello"}'
```

