## pc-agent endpoints

Base: `http://127.0.0.1:3847`

| Method | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| POST | `/task` | Run a Claude task (`X-Agent-Secret`) |
| POST | `/voice/command` | Voice command (local) |
| POST | `/voice/speak-async` | Fire-and-forget TTS (Bearer auth) |
| GET | `/voice/ping` | Health |
| GET | `/voice/stream` | SSE |
| GET | `/friday` | Web UI |
| GET/PUT | `/settings/echo` | ECHO config |

---

## skill-gateway endpoints

Base: `http://127.0.0.1:3848`

| Method | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| POST | `/alexa` | Alexa webhook |
| POST | `/openclaw/trigger` | Manual trigger |
| POST | `/webhook/evolution` | WhatsApp |
| POST | `/internal/speak` | Direct TTS |
| POST | `/internal/stop-all-media` | Stop music / optional TTS locks |
